  "prompt": "How long does it take to open a savings bank account in ICICI bank?",
  "response": "Opening a savings bank account in ICICI Bank can vary in duration based on several factors, such as whether you are applying online or visiting a branch. Generally, the process can take anywhere from a few minutes to a couple of hours. \n\n1. **Online Application:** If you apply online through the ICICI Bank website or mobile app, the process can be quite quick. You may be able to complete the application in 15-30 minutes, depending on the information you need to provide and any verification steps. Account activation may take a few hours to a couple of days.\n\n2. **In-Branch Application:** If you visit a branch to open the account, the process might take longer, potentially an hour or more, depending on the number of customers in the branch and the complexity of your application.\n\nIn both cases, having all the required documents (like ID proof, address proof, and a passport-sized photograph) ready can speed up the process. Always check with the bank directly for the most accurate and current information regarding account opening procedures.",
